         <abstract>
            <p>The modified moments of the weight functions $w(x) = x^\rho(1 - x)^\alpha \ln(1/x)$, on $\lbrack 0, 1 \rbrack$, with respect to the shift Jacobi polynomials $P^{\ast^(\alpha,\beta)}_n(x) = P^{(\alpha,\beta)}_n(2x - 1)$, and $w_p(x) = x^\rho e^{-x}(\ln x)^p, p = 1, 2$, on $\lbrack 0, \infty)$, with respect to the generalized Laguerre polynomials $L^{(\alpha)}_n(x)$, are explicitly evaluated.</p>
          </abstract>
